      "lesson title": "Using AI with Customer Data Safely",
      "order": 1,
      "Description": "This lesson introduces practical, straightforward guidance for anyone who works with customer or client data and wants to use AI tools responsibly. You will learn how to identify what types of information require extra care, and how to apply simple guardrails before sharing anything with an AI system. The lesson covers common mistakes people make when using AI in a professional context, and how to avoid putting your customers or your organisation at risk. By the end, you will feel confident making better decisions about when and how to use AI safely as part of your everyday work.",
