          "number": 5,
          "slidetitle": "Minimising Risk in Practice",
          "subtitle": "Practical steps to protect customer data",
          "slidecontent": "• Remove or replace names, emails, and account numbers before pasting data into any AI tool\n• Anonymise first, always\n• Use fictional or scrambled examples when testing AI features during setup or training\n• Check your organisation's policy before sharing any customer information with a third-party AI service\n• Treat AI input fields like public spaces, not private ones\n• Keep a record of what data types you have used with AI tools, in case of a later audit"
