          "slidetitle": "Red Flags to Watch For",
          "subtitle": "Warning signs that demand your attention",
          "slidecontent": "• AI requests full customer databases\n• Output includes real names unexpectedly\n• No opt-out option offered\n• Tool stores your inputs automatically\n• Vague privacy policy or none"
