        {
          "number": 8,
          "slidetitle": "What to Remember",
          "subtitle": "Keep these principles close at hand.",
          "slidecontent": "• Never paste real customer data into a public or unverified AI tool\n• Anonymise first, then prompt\n• Always check your organisation's policy before using AI with any client information\n• If in doubt, leave it out\n• Treat AI tools like any other third-party software, with the same data-handling care\n• Start small, review the results, and build confidence gradually before scaling up your use"
